      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i tried checking the caliper but it looks okay to me, doesn't seem stuck. do you think it could be a sensor? also the sound is really sharp and intermittent, almost like a sudden piercing noise rather than a constant grinding. does that change anything?",
